+## 🎯 Requested New Features
+
+### Feature 1: Decimal Time Entry for Manual Edits
+
+**Current Behavior:**
+- Manual time entry uses start/end times (HH:MM AM/PM format)
+- Duration calculated automatically
+
+**Requested:**
+- Allow direct entry of decimal hours (e.g., 2.5 hours, 0.75 hours)
+- Useful for quick entries when exact start/end times unknown
+
+**Implementation Notes:**
+- Add option in manual entry form: "Enter duration directly"
+- Input field for decimal hours (validate: positive number, max 24)
+- Calculate start_time = date + current time, end_time = start + duration
+- Update `gui.py` manual entry section
+- Update `models.py` TimeEntry.add_manual_entry() to accept duration option
+
+**Priority:** Medium  
+**Complexity:** Low (form update + calculation logic)
+
+---
+
+### Feature 2: Invoice Preview & Approval Mode
+
+**Current Behavior:**
+- Generate invoice → immediately marks time entries as billed
+- No verification step before billing
+- Can't undo billing once saved
+
+**Requested:**
+- **Preview Mode** - Generate invoice WITHOUT marking as billed
+- **Approval Step** - User must explicitly approve before billing
+- **Audit Opportunity** - Review items, edit if needed, then approve
+- **Cancel Option** - Discard preview without billing
+
+**Implementation Notes:**
+
+**Phase 1: Preview Mode**
+```python
+# New flow:
+1. User selects entries → "Generate Preview"
+2. Display invoice in preview mode (entries NOT marked billed)
+3. Show warning: "PREVIEW MODE - Not yet billed"
+4. Allow edits to invoice items
+5. Two buttons: "Approve & Bill" or "Cancel Preview"
+```
+
+**Phase 2: Approval**
+```python
+# On "Approve & Bill":
+1. Show confirmation dialog
+2. Mark entries as billed
+3. Save to billing_history
+4. Generate PDF
+5. Update UI to show [BILLED] status
+```
+
+**Phase 3: Cancel**
+```python
+# On "Cancel Preview":
+1. Clear invoice preview
+2. Entries remain unbilled
+3. User can regenerate with different selections
+```
+
+**UI Changes:**
+- `gui.py` invoice tab: Add "PREVIEW MODE" banner
+- Change button labels: "Generate Invoice" → "Generate Preview"
+- Add "Approve & Bill" button (only active in preview mode)
+- Add "Cancel Preview" button
+- Disable PDF export until approved
+
+**Database Changes:**
+- NO changes needed - just delay the `mark_entries_billed()` call
+- Only execute after "Approve & Bill" clicked
+
+**Priority:** HIGH (prevents accidental billing errors)  
+**Complexity:** Medium (UI changes + workflow logic)
+
