+## ⚙️ Key Technical Details
+
+### Critical Code Sections:
+
+**Database Initialization** (`db_manager.py` lines 14-49)
+- Must initialize `self.conn = None` FIRST
+- Use `@contextmanager` with try/finally for `get_connection()`
+- No duplicate class/method declarations
+
+**Config Path** (`config.py`)
+- Uses raw string `r"..."` for Windows paths with spaces
+- Fallback to local database if Google Drive not found
+- Currently hardcoded to desktop path
+
+**GUI Database Usage** (`gui.py` line 14-60)
+- Accepts `db_path` parameter in `__init__`
+- Passes path to `DatabaseManager(db_path)`
+- Has error handling with traceback
+
+### Import Structure:
+```python
+# All files use:
+from db_manager import DatabaseManager  # NOT "database"
+from config import DB_PATH
+```
+
+### Database Schema:
+- SQLite with FTS (Full Text Search)
+- 8 main tables + views
+- Automatic schema migration on startup
+- Billing history tracks invoiced entries
